===Talking to Metzli, Teokan of Ranul===
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' I know your face. I have seen it a thousand times before.
* '''Player:''' Er... I think you must have me confused with someone else. We've never met.
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Yes... and no. This is our first encounter, and yet I know you better than most. You wear the face of my only true companion. You wear the face of death.
* '''Player:''' Your only companion is death? You should probably get out more.
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' You jest, as your kind often do. Is that how you drown out their screams, I wonder? Is that how you hide your pain?
* '''Player:''' Well things got deep very quickly. Is this how you normally introduce yourself to someone?
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Few seek an introduction with the Sect of Ranul. They spend their days in Ralos' light. The darkness hides an inevitable truth that they prefer to shy away from.
* '''Player:''' Right... So who actually are you?
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' I am Metzli, Teokan of Ranul. You I already know. You are the one that saved the life of my counterpart.
* '''Player:''' Teokan? So there are two of you?
* '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Yes. As Teokan of Ranul, I lead the Sect of Ranul. My counterpart, Servius, leads the Church of Ralos.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I'm meant to be meeting Prince Itzla here.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm meant to be meeting Prince Itzla here.
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Yes you are. He is speaking with Servius, down in the crypt. Not a place you'd normally find the Teokan of Ralos, but the Prince desired the privacy only Ranul can offer.
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Could you tell me more about the Church of Ralos?}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|Could you tell me more about the Sect of Ranul?}}
*** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|I'd better head down there.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'd better head down there.
*** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Farewell.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Could you tell me more about the Church of Ralos?}}
** '''Player:''' Could you tell me more about the Church of Ralos?
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Those who worship the light can be found throughout these lands, and it is the Church of Ralos that leads their worship.
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' If you wish to learn more, you should seek out Servius or one of his Teoki. They will be better placed to guide you than I, for my duty is one of darkness, not light.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Could you tell me more about the Sect of Ranul?}}
** '''Player:''' Could you tell me more about the Sect of Ranul?
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Ralos' light can be found all across Varlamore, but when that light fades, there is only one who can guide us through the darkness.
** '''Player:''' Ranul?
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Yes. You will not find many worshippers of Ranul in your travels. Indeed, many choose to hide from him their whole lives, but no matter what, we will all meet Ranul in the end.
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' When the sun sets, it is he that will guide us. He will lead us through the Gates of Mictl to where we may finally rest. The duty of the Sect of Ranul is to ensure that all are prepared for that journey.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|I'd better get going.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd better get going.
** '''Metzli, Teokan of Ranul:''' Farewell.
** {{tact|end}}

